Package: SPIAT3D
Title: Spatial image analysis of tissues in 3D
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Le", , "david.le@petermac.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0008-1215-4230"))
Description: SPIAT-3D has a diverse range of spatial metrics which use the 
              x, y, z and cell type identity of each cell to analyse 3D spatial 
              tissue data. Includes 3D cell colocalization metrics, spatial 
              heterogeneity metrics and clustering algorithms.
